thread.title: As Serena Williams Continues Her Comeback, Venus Williams Moves on at Indian Wells

author: Tom Perrotta
title: As Serena Williams Continues Her Comeback, Venus Williams Moves on at Indian Wells
text:
After 14 months away from professional tennis, Serena Williams, now a mother, is healthy and hitting hard, but not enough to beat her sister Venus.
In a marquee third-round match Monday evening in Indian Wells, Calif., Venus beat Serena 6-3, 6-4. The beginning of the match was close, with several deuce games and tense moments. But from then on Venus made fewer mistakes and took a commanding lead. Overall Serena made 41 unforced errors to Venusâ€™s 19.
